item.title: Lizzo is the hip-hop artist you need for 2016
item.description:
Lizzo is the hip-hop artist you need for 2016

Despite what Floridians might tell you, there are many great things about Minneapolis and the Twin Cities area: It isn't "all snow, all the time." The parties - like the Cocktailian at The Depot - are among the best around. The Walker Art Center always has something inspiring on (including an exhibition of British humor). Hell, even in winter it's worth going there just for the St. Paul Carnival.Â
